TO BEGIN:
Place all letter tiles（字母片） in the pouch（袋子）,
or turn all letters face down（正面朝下） at the side of the board and shuffle（洗牌）.

Draw（抽牌） for the first play.
The player drawing the letter nearest（最靠近） the beginning of the alphabet
play first.

A blank tile（空片） beats any letter.

Put the exposed（已经暴漏地） letters back and re-shuffle.

Each player in order then draws seven new letters（抽取7张字母片） and
places them on their rack（架子）.